Package: mutType
Title: Determine the mutation type for a set of single nucleotide variants in a genome with mutType package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alessandro", "Giulivo", , "alessandro.giulivo@mail.polimi.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The mutType package takes a set of mutations (single nucleotide variants, SNVs) in VCF format, and determines for each mutation the corresponding mutation type.
